---
Source:
  - Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
    ISBN: 978-1571746931
By: Sri Chinmoy
Page: 147
---
Finally have I realized that I am what I have been seeking.
I have found bliss is the realm beyond the knower and the known.
Mind, form, will, thought -- all have ceased.
The foal has been reached and the truth has been revealed.
I am the way -- the soul of God. My cosmic play has ended.
